name: Space skill test
description:
SPACE SKILLS TEST is a hardcore 3D game for 1 player.

 The game is designed to test your parkour skills.

 This challenge features beautiful space graphics as well as interesting and popular types of parkour, including rock climbing.

 The game has 3 regular levels, 2 temporary levels, as well as cards with special tests.

 Test your skills, have fun!

Controls :

  • WASD = move
  • Space = jump
  • Shift = run 
  •  E = action
